# To enable the cron: `gh auth refresh -h github.com -s workflow` then
# `git add -f .github/workflows && git commit -m "add workflows" && git push`.
# (Or add pipeline.yml via GitHub -> Actions -> New workflow, which isn't scope-gated.)
